source.name: FY07  Veterans Compensation and Pension by County
source.description: The Compensation and Pension by County dataset is a count of the number of veterans receiving disability compensation or pension payments from the Department of Veterans Affairs.  The data is reported at the county level, by age group and by % disability rating for each state plus recipients in Guam, Philippines and Puerto Rico.
